issues.description: The problem statement’s UML specifies addGuestStudents(int, String) but the solution’s Lecture class defines addGuestStudents with only an int parameter, omitting the String reason. This mismatch in parameters will prevent students from matching the specified signature and tests.
issues.suggested_fix: Modify the solution’s addGuestStudents method signature to include the String reason parameter (e.g. addGuestStudents(int numberOfNewGuestStudents, String reason)) and update its implementation accordingly.
